// MardukElevated.rc
//
// Embeds the side-by-side application manifest into the executable.
// Resource name 1 (CREATEPROCESS_MANIFEST_RESOURCE_ID) and resource type
// 24 (RT_MANIFEST) are the magic IDs that the Windows loader scans for
// when launching a process. Both MSVC's rc.exe and MinGW's windres
// understand this directive identically.
1 24 "MardukElevated.manifest"
